<p><b>Botanical names</b>. When publishing papers that describe a new botanical taxon name, PLOS aims to comply with the
  requirements of the International Code of Botanical Nomenclature (ICBN). Following from a test case (Knapp S [2010] PLOS ONE. doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0010502) and in association with the <a href="http://www.ipni.org/">International Plant Names Index</a> (IPNI), the
